data.text:
Free local delivery is available for orders over $120 within Singapore. For orders under $120, we charge $10 for local delivery.

You can skip the shipping fees with free local pickup at our vinyl

record listening cafe. After placing your order and selecting local

pickup at checkout, your order will be prepared and ready for pick up

within 1-3 business days. We will send you an email when your order is ready along with instructions.

Our shipping policy page can be visited here.

All used vinyl records are carefully graded visually. Here’s a friendly guide to our grading system:

Excellent: This record looks almost new, plays beautifully without any significant surface loss of sound quality. Its cover and any extras, like lyric sheets, booklets, or posters, are also in top-notch condition, showing only minimal signs of handling.

Very Good: You might find some surface marks or a few light scratches, but these do not affect the listening experience. The cover and any additional items might show a bit of wear, like light creases or minor edge scuffs.

Good: You might notice some sound quality changes or mild character marks. The cover and any inserts may have some folding, edge scuffing, spine splits, or a bit of discoloration.
